author: wsmoak
msg: Allow the example apps to be built with specified versions of Tomahawk and the MyFaces impl.
Introduce a property for the MyFaces version number, set to the current snapshot, which can be overridden with -Dmyfaces=x.x.x on the mvn command line.

Add profiles for the tomahawk version.  Exactly one will be activated by the 'tomahawk' property.  In its absence, the current snapshot will be used.  Otherwise, use -Dtomahawk=x.x.x to specify a version.
